      "date": "2011-12-13 03:35:22.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nI actually prefer you add LMV device if there are no LMV device in the config log, instead of moving ELC to mdc, which might bring trouble to DNE. Thanks.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
