    {
      "id": "f444786c15dd36898857b4d8f42a9add828ee99d",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 101,
        "name": "Lai Siyao",
        "email": "lai.siyao@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "laisiyao"
      },
      "date": "2011-12-13 06:43:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nOleg, what's your opinion on this? I think both way are okay, and DNE has chosen to create missing config in upgrade, if 1.8 -> 2.1 should follow this policy, I will make another patch.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "deca4d6aba294f853140c4ce1f68382a033cb111",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 112,
        "name": "Oleg Drokin",
        "email": "green@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "green"
      },
      "date": "2011-12-13 08:10:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nI think having mostly dead code that only operates when this is 1.8 to 2.x interoperability is bad idea as it would be rarely executed with a possibility of rotting soon.\nAs such creating lmv if there is not one is probably better.",
